data.title: Convert Central Time to Central Time
data.meta_description: Quickly convert Central European Time (CET) to Central European Summer Time (CEST) with this easy-to-use, modern time zone converter.
data.text:
Converting CET to CEST

This time zone converter lets you visually and very quickly convert CET to CEST and vice-versa. Simply mouse over the colored hour-tiles and glance at the hours selected by the column... and done!
